\u0009\u0009\u0009 We always prioritize user experience. In order to optimize and improve the system functionality, we sincerely invite you to join us in this endeavor. IHU operation log information, including exceptions, errors, warnings and other information generated during the system operation process, is obtained to help us quickly complete system remote diagnosis.
\u0009\u0009\u0009 We hereby declare that the IHU log information we collect will not be actively associated with your personal information. However, it is not ruled out that the system may contain personal information related to your use during operation. The collection, transmission, and use of this information will also be protected by relevant security technologies.
